code: @Bean public InternalResourceViewResolver viewResolver() {     InternalResourceViewResolver viewResolver = new InternalResourceViewResolver().     viewResolver.setPrefix("/WEB-INF/views/").     viewResolver.setSuffix(".jsp").     return viewResolver. }
